Package org.bonitasoft.engine.bpm.actor

Interface ActorMember

All Superinterfaces:
BonitaObject, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
ActorMemberImpl
public interface ActorMember extends BonitaObject
It is used to map an ActorInstance with the organization. It's possible to map an ActorInstance with a user, or a group, or a role, or a group and a role.
Since:
6.0.0
Author:
Matthieu Chaffotte, Celine Souchet
